### Enhancements

* Add environment specifier plugin support to `conda create --file`. Environment files (YAML, requirements.txt, explicit, etc.) are now parsed via the plugin system, matching `conda env create` behavior. Name and prefix can be read from files when `-n`/`-p` are omitted. (#15573)

